                <dateline>
                    <date ana="#date_undated-inferred-from-chapter-heading" calendar="gregorian"
                        when="1946-10-02T15:30:00+01:00">October 2, 1946, 3:30 p.m.</date>
                </dateline>
                <p rend="flushleft">
                    <gloss target="#t_USDel1">USDel</gloss> (PC) (Journal) 59</p>
                <p>The draft report on military clauses of the Italian treaty was approved without
                        controversy.<note n="68" xml:id="d285fn1">For text of report, C.P.(Plen)
                        Doc. 17, October 5, see <ref target="frus1946v04#pg_412">vol. <hi
